ght="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="吉米·佩奇和黑乌鸦。图片来源：罗斯·半（Ross Halfin）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jimmy-Page-and-The-Black-Crowes.-Credit-Ross-Halfin-JPageBCrowes_2000_020300D-0012-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Jimmy-Page">吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）</a>和<a href="/artists/The-Black-Crowes">黑乌鸦（Black Crowes）</a>已联手演绎了<a href="/artists/Led-Zeppelin">齐佩林（Led Zeppelin</a> ）的《柠檬歌》（The Lemon Song）。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/becoming-led-zeppelin-review-jimmy-page-robert-plant-3835611"><b>“成为LED Zeppelin”评论：英国最爆炸乐队的权威起源故事</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这是标志性摇滚乐队1969年的曲目亮点页面和《黑乌鸦》音乐化学反应的新发掘的现场录音，将歌曲转变为Led Zeppelin的第二张录音室专辑的Edgier版本。他们对这首歌的演绎最初是在2000年的一次音符检查中录制的。</p><p> “柠檬歌”标志着即将推出的吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）和《黑乌鸦》（The Black Crowes）1999年合作专辑“ Live in the Greek&#39;&#39;的Repentede Edition Edition将在即将推出的Reissue Edition中展出的各种未发行的歌曲之一。重新发行定于3月14日通过果园发布，可<a href="https://orcd.co/liveatthegreek2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。 </p><p><iframe title="柠檬歌（Soundcheck）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1EmT-OUtYdI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 1999年10月，在1999年8月在洛杉矶的希腊剧院和琼斯海滩的摇滚摇滚夜晚录制的“吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）和《黑乌鸦：希腊人》（The Black Crowes：Live the Greek），这是传奇的吉他手，黑乌鸦（Black Crowes）看到了LED Zeppelin的曲目从LED Zeppelin的Catalog中转变为具有强大的表演。</p><p>由凯文·雪莉（Kevin Shirley）制作，混合和重新制作的36曲周年纪念专辑以16首以前未发行的歌曲以及独家幕后照片，视频等。</p><p>吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）在新闻稿中谈到重新发行时说：“我真的很期待很快发行吉米·佩奇（Jimmy Page）和1999年音乐会上的《黑乌鸦》（Black Crowes）材料。新混合物捕捉了这些历史性接触的合作，并提供了这些炼金术时刻的完整爆炸性激情和令人兴奋的能量。” </p><figure id="attachment_3842097" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3842097" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3842097" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="直播希腊专辑封面。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Live-At-The-Greek-Album-Cover.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3842097" class="wp-caption-text">直播希腊专辑封面。信用：出版</f